      "html": "The <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-handle/identity/#dfn-observable\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-observable-2\">observable<!---0.927286%--></a> <a data-xref-type=\"_IDL_\" data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"CaptureHandle\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-handle/identity/#dom-capturehandle\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-capturehandle-5\"><code>CaptureHandle<!---0.927286%--></code></a><!---0.927286%--> is re-evaluated for all capturing applications.",
      "rationale": "for",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "For every capturing application for which the new <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-handle/identity/#dfn-observable\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-observable-3\">observable<!---0.927286%--></a> <a data-xref-type=\"_IDL_\" data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"CaptureHandle\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-handle/identity/#dom-capturehandle\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-capturehandle-6\"><code>CaptureHandle<!---0.927286%--></code></a><!---0.927286%-->\n                is different than prior to the call to <!---0.927286%--><a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-xref-type=\"attribute|dict-member|const\" data-link-for=\"MediaDevices\" data-xref-for=\"MediaDevices\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-handle/identity/#dom-mediadevices-setcapturehandleconfig\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-mediadevices-setcapturehandleconfig-9\"><code>setCaptureHandleConfig<!---0.927286%--></code></a><!---0.927286%-->,\n                the user agent <em class=\"rfc2119\">MUST<!---0.927286%--></em> <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" data-cite=\"dom\" data-cite-path=\"/\" data-cite-frag=\"concept-event-fire\" data-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire\">fire an event<!---0.927286%--></a> named <!---0.927286%--><a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-xref-type=\"attribute|dict-member|const\" data-link-for=\"MediaStreamTrack\" data-xref-for=\"MediaStreamTrack\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-handle/identity/#dfn-capturehandlechange\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-capturehandlechange-1\"><code>capturehandlechange<!---0.927286%--></code></a><!---0.927286%-->."
        },
        {
          "html": "The user agent <em class=\"rfc2119\">MUST<!---0.927286%--></em> report the new <a data-link-type=\"dfn|abstract-op\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-handle/identity/#dfn-observable\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-observable-4\">observable<!---0.927286%--></a> <a data-xref-type=\"_IDL_\" data-link-type=\"idl\" data-lt=\"CaptureHandle\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-handle/identity/#dom-capturehandle\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-capturehandle-7\"><code>CaptureHandle<!---0.927286%--></code></a><!---0.927286%--> whenever\n                <!---0.927286%--><a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-xref-type=\"attribute|dict-member|const\" data-link-for=\"MediaStreamTrack\" data-xref-for=\"MediaStreamTrack\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-handle/identity/#dom-mediastreamtrack-getcapturehandle\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-getcapturehandle-1\"><code>getCaptureHandle<!---0.927286%--></code></a><!---0.927286%--> is called."
        }
      ]
    }
